com.glyart.mystral.exceptions.DataAccessException

Packages that use DataAccessException
Package
Description
com.glyart.mystral.database
Contains the implementations of the main functionalities of this library.
com.glyart.mystral.sql
Contains interfaces used by DataOperations and AsyncDataOperations implementations.
These interfaces represent various operations: Connection objects manipulation Generic sql operations Parametrized callbacks Easy exception handling
